    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/865cf122dd16441180d353d9a14f6bf1.poster.avif?t=1770300662\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/865cf122dd16441180d353d9a14f6bf1.webm?t=1770300662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/865cf122dd16441180d353d9a14f6bf1.mp4?t=1770300662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>关于</strong><br>狗狗特攻队是一款精彩的 2D 像素风 platformer 平台游戏。游戏中，你将化身一只名为帕布洛的小狗，使用钩爪完成各种高难度关卡！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/6a623ca1b4c236d7aff07dea8439f5d3.poster.avif?t=1770300662\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/6a623ca1b4c236d7aff07dea8439f5d3.webm?t=1770300662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345860/extras/6a623ca1b4c236d7aff07dea8439f5d3.mp4?t=1770300662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特征</strong><br><br>🐶 绝妙的动作——跳跃！摇摆！收集宝石！小狗！钩爪！驾驶小船！还有最棒的事情，撸狗！<br><br>🐕  个风采各异的世界——驾驶小船，探索地图中的 6 个世界、33 个关卡，寻找隐藏的珍宝，深入神秘的地区，赢下史诗般的 boss 战，学习更高级的奖励秘籍<br><br>🐕‍🦺 冲啊，小狗！——化身使用钩爪的小狗帕布洛，与众多有趣的角色一起，开始一场愉快的冒险！与你乐观无畏的冒险同伴们一起航行，从机器人霸主纳尔手中拯救世界<br><br>🐩 随心畅玩——使用各种特异的收藏品，或选择竞速模式，磨练你的闯关技巧；利用游戏内置的不同选项，享受无限制的闯关体验——只要你开心，想怎么玩就怎么玩<br><br>🪝 大胆而独特——色彩选择大胆而丰富的像素风格令小狗的闯关动作从始至终生动有趣，再加上独特而新颖的配乐，一定让你欲罢不能",
